title: War of the Roses: He Actually Wants Her to be Cheating?
description: Harry is REALLY bad at confrontation and has some suspicions his girlfriend might be cheating.  He actually hopes she is because he wants to end things so he does War of the Roses to see if she's cheating so then they would have to break up.  Does it work out that way?
